component COMP-003 "Assembler"
  responsibility: Resolve the validated system model into context
                  suitable for consumption by an AI coding agent.
                  For each affected component, assemble its interfaces,
                  allocated requirements, and linked test specifications
                  into a single coherent output. Only assemble context
                  for components affected by model changes.
  depends_on: COMP-001, COMP-002, COMP-006
  satisfies: BP-004, BP-008
